Brookstone Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 3:49 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Brookstone Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Brookstone Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning services. It primarily provides its services to individuals. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals and pension and profit sharing plans. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in alternative investment markets including precious metals, currencies, energy, commodities, REIT's, variable annuities, and structured products. The firm invests in mutual funds and exchange traded funds. For the equity portion of its portfolio, it pr...
Brookstone Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning services. It primarily provides its services to individuals. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals and pension and profit sharing plans. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in alternative investment markets including precious metals, currencies, energy, commodities, REIT's, variable annuities, and structured products. The firm invests in mutual funds and exchange traded funds. For the equity portion of its portfolio, it primarily invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified sectors. For the fixed income portion of its portfolio, the firm invests in diversified portfolio of investments including government bonds, high yield bonds, market-linked certificates of deposit, municipal bonds, investment-grade domestic bonds, short-term reserves, foreign bonds, and inflation-protected bonds. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index, Canterbury Volatility Index, Wide Moat Focus Index, MSCI USA Catholic Values Index, and MSCI KLD 400 Social Index. It employs a combination of in-house and external research to make its investments. Brookstone Capital Management, LLC was founded in 2006 and is based in Wheaton, Illinois.
Detailed Description


